<%= render :partial => "partials/page_header", :locals => {:title => "About"} %>
<p class="lead">
  <strong>Virtual Town Square</strong> is a place to keep up and discuss local issues in the New River Valley.
</p>

<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span6 well" style="height: 250px">
    <h3>Local Issues</h3>
    <p class="lead">
      We collect Local News, Blogs, Twitter and Facebook Discussions happening in New River Valley, so that you can come here to keep up with important local issues and developments.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="span6 well" style="height: 250px">
    <h3>Participate</h3>
    <p class="lead">
      Post articles, comment and like news stories. Share news on your social networks on Twitter, Facebook, Google+ or elsewhere.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span6 well" style="height: 250px">
    <h3>Research</h3>
      <p class="lead">
        This project is being actively developed as part of research at <a href="http://vt.edu">Virginia Tech</a>. Learn more about it on the <%= link_to "About Research", research_url %> page. It is opensource and available on <a href='http://github.com/colloki/colloki'>Github</a>.
      </p>
  </div>
  <div class="span6 well" style="height: 250px">
    <h3>Local Blogger or Publisher?</h3>
    <p class="lead">
      <%= render :partial => "partials/about/local_publisher" %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
